parameters:
\SE[33]I think it's urgent, so... um, excuse me for barging in
without knocking...!

\SE[102]He's still sleeping as usual... How can he sleep through
that loud noise and vibration...? \SE[100]As expected of
Lunaroa... She's truly something...

\SE[99]No, there's still a possibility that it was just my
mishearing... Let's observe quietly to see if he's really using
magic... \SE[58]I apologize for falsely accusing him of 'false
charges'...

\SE[22]\!\SE[102]\SM[pop]... Ah, I've become all warm and fuzzy
again! \. It's the same situation as last time...! \!\SE[100]
This calls for a prompt response...!!

\SE[99]But, what should I do...? Last time, it was fine because
Lunaroa grew a penis... \SE[58]But this time, since it's not
there, how should I approach it...?

\SE[116]H-Hii...!? \. That has started! \!\SE[33]If I keep
dawdling, the end will begin!

\SE[99]No, last time it was that from here... \!\SE[100]It might
be the right choice to observe the situation... If it happens
again, we can use the same solution as last time...

\SE[116]W-What is this...? Could it be...? \SE[33]To think
that... it's me...!? \SE[33]To end up in a situation like this...
♡
